4.56 OEGetCovalentRadius 
 
   
double OEGetCovalentRadius(unsigned int elemno)
    
Return the covalent radius of the element specified by the given
atomic number.  The covalent radius of an atom is typically used in
bonding calculations, such as the function  OEDetermineConnectivity .
A value of zero is returned for elements other than those commonly found
in organic molecules.  The actual values are those prescribed by the
Cambridge Crystallographic Database.

  

  
          
     
        
